description: Stunning 4 bedroom duplex loft in full-service South Boston building. Newly constructed, 14 W. Broadway is a concierge building featuring grand porte-cochere entryway w/ valet parking, fitness center & one of the largest roofdecks in Boston. This duplex has a gracious foyer that leads to an open / living dining room w/ approx. 20' ceilings, double-height windows & private balcony. Kitchen features Quartzite counters, Sub Zero & Wolf appliances & large island w/ wine fridge. Adjacent family room w/ full bath makes the living level a seamless entertaining space. Upstairs, the bedroom level has a large primary bedroom w/ walk-in closet & ensuite bath w/ marble tile & glass shower. 2 guest bedrooms share a large bathroom. Plenty of closet space, custom window treatments, dark wood floors, Sonos audio & laundry room. Steps to restaurants, shops, coffee, hotel & Broadway T Station. Easily accessible to Seaport, South End, Financial District & major transporation.
